Package game.views

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BackgroundObjectView
    Class that determines how the background objects are displayed in the game window.
    EnemyView
    Class that determines how the enemy objects are displayed in the game window.
    GameView
    Class for creating the canvas (aka "drawing board") of the game.
    MenuView
    Class holds variables which belongs to the menus.
    MessageView
    Class for creating the animated message for user inside a HBox which is placed in the center of the window.
    PlayerView
    Class that determines how the player object is displayed in the game window.
